+// Electron: weak so the generated node_snapshot.cc (linked into the shipped
+// Electron framework) can override it with the real embedded snapshot, while
+// node_mksnapshot and other build tools that link libnode (which always
+// includes this stub) still get the no-snapshot fallback. This is the only
